description:
GQ grooming director Garrett Munce discusses why men want permission to talk about beauty, the death of the term "metrosexual," and the reason he's over the lumberjack look. We also share the science behind topicals with CBD (cannabidiol), discuss Bobbi Brown's new wellness line, and get into the history (and current popularity) of cica balms.
